Module org.nasdanika.html.model.bootstrap
Package org.nasdanika.html.model.bootstrap

Interface Spacing

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
SpacingImpl
public interface Spacing extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Spacing'. Spacing - padding or margin. Specifies size, location, and breakpoint.

The following features are supported:

  • Size
  • Breakpoint
  • Top
  • Bottom
  • Left
  • Right
  • X
  • Y
See Also:
  • BootstrapPackage.getSpacing()
